类 ChargingSummary

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.everon.evbox.chargingstore.models.ChargingSummary

  • public class ChargingSummary
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a summary of charging sessions for the last minute.
    作者:
    Wang Long

    • 构造器概要

      构造器 
      构造器和说明
      ChargingSummary()
      This constructs a summary of charging session without any field.
      ChargingSummary(long totalCount, long startedCount, long stoppedCount)
      This constructs a summary of charging session with a specified totalCount, startedCount and stoppedCount.
